---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="页面未找到" description="您访问的页面不存在。">
	<section class="py-28 sm:py-40">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6">
			<p class="section-index mb-5">404</p>
			<h1 class="display-title text-4xl sm:text-6xl">迷路了？</h1>
			<p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-md text-lg text-muted">
				抱歉，您访问的页面不存在或已被移除。不如回到首页重新出发。
			</p>
			<a
				href="/"
				class="mt-10 inline-block rounded-full bg-accent px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-accent-hover"
			>
				返回首页
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
